<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="blow-v">blow <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bləʊ/    美 /bloʊ/  </p>
<p>(blew, blown)vi &amp; vt</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(风) 吹；刮：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The wind is <strong>blowing hard</strong> tonight.
今晚刮着大风。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>吹（气）：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The policeman asked the driver to <strong>blow into</strong> an electronic device.
警察要求司机朝一个电子仪器吹气。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>（被）吹动；（被）刮走：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The door <strong>blew open</strong>.
门被吹开了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Her hair was blowing in the breeze. 
她的头发在微风中摇曳</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>吹响；吹奏；鸣响：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Blow your horn. 
鸣响你的喇叭。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The whistle blew for the end of the game. 
比赛结束的哨声吹响了。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.<strong>(使) 爆炸；(使) 破裂：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>blow sth to pieces 
把某物炸成碎片</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The tire blew. 
轮胎爆了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="blow-down">blow down</h3>
<p>1.<strong>刮倒：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The trees blown down in the storm have been moved off the road. 
在暴风雨中刮倒的树木已被移出路面。</p><footer>2008 湖南</footer></div>

<h3 id="blow-out">blow out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>吹灭：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Blow the candle out. 
把蜡烛吹灭。</p></div>

<h3 id="blow-up">blow up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>给…充气；炸毁；爆炸 (explode)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I blew up lots of balloons. 
我吹了很多气球。</p><footer>北师大① – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The terrorists are threatening to blow up the building.
恐怖分子扬言要炸毁这座大楼。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A police officer was killed when his car blew up. 
一名警察在其汽车爆炸时遇难。</p></div></div>